      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "The Independent Elevator Co.,\norganized two months ago with\nSpokane county capital, announces\nthe closing of deal today whereby\nthe company secures all the build\nings of the Inland Mill & Manufac-\nturing Co. and two lots in Railroad\naddition.\n\n\nThe Independent company will\ntake possession April / and expects\nto erect an elevator of 100000\nbushels capacity to be operated in\nconnection with line OF elevators\nto be established throughout the\nInland Empire. In Spokane the\ncompany figures on investing $25..\ncoo in the new elevator. John Wall\nters negotiated the purchase made\nhere."
    }
